{"tid":2248311,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"「突發」我係倫敦搵到條最新戰線","createTime":"2020-10-18T13:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T16:01:02.000Z","uid":191271,"like":15,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1870df7c6bfdd67f377757b992ae9dd675f261ee","tid":2248311,"uid":191271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大家好 好耐冇見<br />\n我爛炒巴，除左將會動用大家之前籌俾我既 5千萬港紙 係倫敦買樓自住之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將會打算發起國際戰線 － <strong><span class=\"orange\">倫敦金眾籌</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n希望到時大家多多支持，展現俾全世界睇我地香港人有幾撚蠢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"458043bf8d6c954d47084bf3f949e1687bff0c07","tid":2248311,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:25:31.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"left\"></p>"},{"pid":"f93d287d8c19e8eeb77035c42cbdbc44fc86d743","tid":2248311,"uid":48083,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"勿回<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立黨=分化撚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UgJp1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UgJp1L.jpg&h=4fb01392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立黨班人出晒名態度惡劣, 無邏輯, 無計劃<br />\n仲要非常小學雞<br />\n獨立黨就係上次同攬炒巴同時搞眾籌嗰個所謂政黨<br />\n結果態度惡劣又無遠見所以比人插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npost出黎既垃圾所謂廣告係poland ball meme<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDd310D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDd310D.jpg&h=8ed9b992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國落廣告宣布中英聯合聲明失效 初稿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301516</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>個垃圾政黨連張垃圾poland ball都可以想攞黎眾籌登報, 獨立黨有幾多斤兩自己諗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n永遠鳩噏無證據支持, 扭曲基本法理, 被質問可行性同進度就機密機密. 從來做唔到實事,只能夠開post當戰績<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vhcVob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vhcVob.png&h=c23e2143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHKIP屌你老母"},{"pid":"cbfd63154405e38e0f6f1c5567015cb2a2d583d4","tid":2248311,"uid":191271,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"f93d287d8c19e8eeb77035c42cbdbc44fc86d743","tid":2248311,"uid":48083,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"勿回<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n香港獨立黨=分化撚<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3UgJp1L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3UgJp1L.jpg&h=4fb01392&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n獨立黨班人出晒名態度惡劣, 無邏輯, 無計劃<br />\n仲要非常小學雞<br />\n獨立黨就係上次同攬炒巴同時搞眾籌嗰個所謂政黨<br />\n結果態度惡劣又無遠見所以比人插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\npost出黎既垃圾所謂廣告係poland ball meme<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zDd310D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzDd310D.jpg&h=8ed9b992&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英國落廣告宣布中英聯合聲明失效 初稿<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1301516\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1301516</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>個垃圾政黨連張垃圾poland ball都可以想攞黎眾籌登報, 獨立黨有幾多斤兩自己諗</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n永遠鳩噏無證據支持, 扭曲基本法理, 被質問可行性同進度就機密機密. 從來做唔到實事,只能夠開post當戰績<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vhcVob.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vhcVob.png&h=c23e2143&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nHKIP屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-18T13:28:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\">處哥 好耐冇見<br />\n反完美國旗後 終於見到你 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"9c